                            "target_lang_translations": {
                                "en": "The monk carefully picked up the ancient <w>Book of Canons</w> bound in leather."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Для вечерней службы священник попросил принести <w>канонник</w> из библиотеки.",
                            "target_lang_translations": {
                                "en": "For the evening service, the priest asked to bring the <w>Book of Canons</w> from the library."
